From 683d17673cdca1ef3e4e019bea05c8d72f71915d Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: dario-silva-se <dario.dsn.erp@gmail.com>
Date: Thu, 18 Jun 2026 12:56:47 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 1/2] =?UTF-8?q?fix:=20UI=20improvements=20=E2=80=94=20i18n?=
 =?UTF-8?q?,=20layout,=20chart=20visibility,=20connection=20status?=
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

- i18n: default to pt-BR regardless of navigator.language; remove
  navigator from detection order so headless/CI envs don't fall back
  to English. Users can still override via localStorage.
- Sidebar: add whitespace-nowrap to appTagline so "ENTERPRISE COMMAND"
  never wraps to two lines in the brand header.
- ConnectionHealthCard: replace uniform secondary border with
  semantic colours — amber for expiring tokens, red for errors.
  Makes YouTube warning state immediately distinguishable from healthy.
- PerformanceChart: increase bar opacity (20→40%) and border opacity
  (40→60%) so bars are legible against the dark background.
- ResultsSummaryCard: increase tile padding (p-md→p-lg), add min-height,
  move trend indicator to a coloured pill badge, remove redundant overlap
  in the value row.
- index.html: switch Material Symbols font-display from swap to block
  to prevent icon name text from flashing during load.

Co-Authored-By: leanderson <leanderson.dario.silva@gmail.com>
